Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down a difficult road\Nfilled with endless struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are going\Nfollowing someone else's map?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An insightful crow comes along\Nto tear up the map
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your eyes and\Ntake a look at the truth (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to lose,\Nso let's GO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh!\NJust go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage, Forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarutobi…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least this sword…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a fitting end for somebody like you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has mastered\Nthe Way of the Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like my arms are burning…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we call off our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the Barrier.\NWe’ll head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes! 					– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Release! 					– Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s released!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Lord Hokage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Spider Web Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An adhesive type of string\Nfilled with Chakra…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi! They’re on the move!\NDo we go after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make a move without\Nany data on the situation up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will get caught in\Nthe enemy’s trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m totally aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But regardless of whether\Nthere is a trap or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can’t let the enemy get away\Nat a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the way of the Leaf Shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…are you just going to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did know, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about time that\Nwe made a retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to run away\Nfrom me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we show our cards,\Nthey’re most likely going to be copied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't seem like you’ve completely\Nmastered that eye like the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temari…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kankuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m leaving Sakura with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is…this guy so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My existence will not disappear…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not disappear!\NI cannot disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to talk to that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there! That’s him…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster! Monster! Monster…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s him… Don’t get involved, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them, I’m just a relic of the past\Nwho they want to see disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did I have in this life,\Nwhy did I keep living?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that time, I thought of myself that I…\Nno, that is what I had to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then knew that\Nit was the most painful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I… that my existence didn’t matter\Nto anyone else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of…being all alone…\Nreally is unbearable, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you feel…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why,\Nbut I completely understand that it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ve met people who are\Nvery important to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t allow those important people…\Nto get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I will stop you even if\Nthat means…that I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that you can fight so much\Nfor other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They saved me from the hell\Nof being all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They accepted me for who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why…they are important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a heart that desires to serve\Na precious person who is close to oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to love and watch over that person…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why he is so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough, Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy’s Chakra must\Nhave been depleted as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura’s sand crumbled\Na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve had enough… Stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never seen Gaara in such\Na weakened state before…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto Uzumaki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE\N							One of these days, even I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temari… Kankuro…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? 					– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t worry about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky has started to weep as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will begin the memorial service
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Third Hokage,\Nwho lost his life in this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the other victims\Nof this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s started…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,\Nall we could do was just watch…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Old Man Hokage have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s already been a year…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:14:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not easy to laugh\Nhiding your sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from your teacher that\Nyou’re the center of laughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not sad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a very honorable thing for\Na Shinobi to die doing their duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and mom sacrificed their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect this village\Nfrom the Demon Fox…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the child of the heroes!\NI’m not sad to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, these are tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you’re curled up\Nholding your knees by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re not alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja of the Hidden Leaf Village\Nhave the will of fire…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will of fire…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the strong will to protect\Nthe Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they have this will of fire,\Neverybody in this village are all family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka… I wonder if you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Hayate…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage’s funeral\Nhas already started. Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kakashi, is it for Obito…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re always thinking of\Nan excuse for your tardiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should just come earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do…from early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just that,\Nwhenever I come here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to punish myself\Nfor being such a fool in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobi, no matter what kind\Nof situation they are in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cannot show their emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must always prioritize your mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never shed a tear in\Nany kind of situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do people risk their own lives\Nfor other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one person dies…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their past, their present life, and their future\Ndisappear along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people die doing their duty\Nand fighting in battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And shockingly easily, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who pass away also\Nhave dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone has something else,\Njust as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parents, siblings, friends, lovers…\NThose who are dear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They trust each other and help each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people whom they’ve cherished\Nsince the day they were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that string which connects\Nthose people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,becomes stronger and\Nthicker as time goes by…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be explained by logic…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who hold those strings just do it,\Nbecause it’s important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I kind of get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like he just died for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left us something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you’ll eventually understand\None of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I kind of get that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain’s stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Third Hokage,\Nthe will of fire you spoke of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seems to have been passed on\Nto the young Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame in their hearts\Nwhich you lit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will burn bright and strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will shine upon this village,\Nand watch over and protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will become a new Hokage…\None of these days…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did manage to avoid annihilation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems the damage\Nis pretty extensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village that was once\Nat the height of its glory…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have lingering affections\Nfor your old home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cycle of hardship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside, we were crying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one thing we won't give up\Nis the dream we've chosen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secondary role,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a role in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reaching for that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us stay centered,\Nlet us stay true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe hung on without giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe kept coming back up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe believed and dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe've seen fools
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ritual ends, and morning mist\Nwill be covering all soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:22:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that white mist,\Nthe shadow quietly sharpens its fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It awakens childhood memory,\Ndisappointment, ire, and resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cog wheel named destiny\Nslowly begins to turn…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Return of the Morning Mist”
